{"id": 2224, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得，人们在处理日常冲突时都容易走上哪些歪路？", "description": "就没有“撕破脸”和“当包子”之外的解决问题方式么？（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 11716, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180314172112MdBQ6WOwZuDNvJRU.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-14T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3853, "title": "你觉得，人们在处理日常冲突时都容易走上哪些歪路？", "content": "日常生活中，人们面对和处理冲突的方式有哪些不合理的地方？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 270455, "content": "一定要分胜负输赢", "image": "img/option/option/20180314120615z6DyE8ZaiMOATnUe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270456, "content": "谁声音更大、情绪更激动或者更伤心，谁就更有理", "image": "img/option/option/20180314120642ynEkYVNap31esIKQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270460, "content": "靠拉拢多数人支持证明自己是对的", "image": "img/option/option/20180314121035EwFcgp6VQOADN4ZX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270500, "content": "对人不对事，“你和我争，还不就是不爽我故意找茬”", "image": "img/option/option/20180314141432NU2gu9kOScr6WfQJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270502, "content": "记仇，“这次跟我有争执，以后也不要当朋友了”", "image": "img/option/option/20180314141556gJzVo83p0ZLbrUiy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270503, "content": "分歧一定是不好的，宁愿忍耐或暗讽也不要吵起来", "image": "img/option/option/20180314141738rZNnXSCQPx9TksR0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270505, "content": "总想着大事化了，“这个问题不重要放一放吧”", "image": "img/option/option/20180314142101ARkp7C3wFl1fgitz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 270517, "content": "把两个人之间的矛盾公开到朋友圈/微博", "image": "img/option/option/201803141502145QdoGBvmEq8jtKcL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}